{"title":"哨所婚礼（外一首）","authors":["刘素英"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨所婚礼（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘素英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰凌凌，雪挂挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传喜讯，放光华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长的新娘到哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身瑞雪白花花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长见了哈哈笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老天为我送婚纱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士见了直嚷嚷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花新娘就是她！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送喜糖，端热茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新嫂子，个个夸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一顿饺子是喜宴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几座冰雕庆婚嫁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂子问这里苦不苦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士立正齐回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你到哨所办婚礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们更爱这个家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈到雪山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈爬上了雪山营区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿见她披一身雪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边关迎来了慈母的火热心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军营里展现的却是冰凌树挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰凌是迎接您的仪仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树挂是欢迎您的插花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈听了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍俊不禁笑出了声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逗得小鸟儿也叽叽喳喳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山生活苦不苦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是冰山上的雪莲花。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}